# Web Server with PHP Support

step1 - Before running the server, make sure you have the following installed:

- Python 3.x
- PHP (go to php.ini
    check line 697
    ;enable_post_data_reading = On)
step 2 - extract the zip file
step 3 - start the "pyhton server.py"
step 4 - By default, the server listens on http://127.0.0.1:2728/.
step 5 - in / directory there is the option to redirect to the html form
step 6 - after submitting the form you will be redirected to the php script